[
  {
    "text": "You cannot defeat me. The rot will",
    "start": 3.76,
    "duration": 6.92
  },
  {
    "text": "consume you all.",
    "start": 6.879,
    "duration": 3.801
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 18.34,
    "duration": 3.19
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 25.02,
    "duration": 3.21
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 33.99,
    "duration": 5.729
  },
  {
    "text": "dear with me. Ready?",
    "start": 35.2,
    "duration": 4.519
  },
  {
    "text": "You think you've won? The rot will",
    "start": 53.039,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "spread until all life dies. Good luck",
    "start": 55.84,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "surviving in the new world you helped",
    "start": 59.039,
    "duration": 5.961
  },
  {
    "text": "create.",
    "start": 62.0,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Heat. Heat.",
    "start": 93.84,
    "duration": 3.08
  },
  {
    "text": "It seems things have gone from bad to",
    "start": 106.159,
    "duration": 3.6
  },
  {
    "text": "worse.",
    "start": 108.72,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": ">> If we don't do something, all the",
    "start": 109.759,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "animals will die. We should build a new",
    "start": 111.84,
    "duration": 4.4
  },
  {
    "text": "base, a home.",
    "start": 114.56,
    "duration": 4.8
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You're right, friends. Owl, can I count",
    "start": 116.24,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "on your support?",
    "start": 119.36,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": ">> My support? I should be the leader of",
    "start": 120.56,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": "this operation.",
    "start": 123.6,
    "duration": 3.199
  },
  {
    "text": ">> We don't have time to argue. Let's put",
    "start": 124.56,
    "duration": 4.559
  },
  {
    "text": "it to a vote. High vote, dear monster.",
    "start": 126.799,
    "duration": 3.921
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Second.",
    "start": 129.119,
    "duration": 2.081
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Same.",
    "start": 130.72,
    "duration": 1.76
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yeah.",
    "start": 131.2,
    "duration": 3.759
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Fine. But if things go sideways, don't",
    "start": 132.48,
    "duration": 4.96
  },
  {
    "text": "blame me.",
    "start": 134.959,
    "duration": 7.64
  },
  {
    "text": "All right, everyone. Let's build a base.",
    "start": 137.44,
    "duration": 5.159
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 144.17,
    "duration": 3.19
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 162.64,
    "duration": 3.2
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 170.38,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "Dear monster, that lightning seems post.",
    "start": 179.36,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Perhaps we shouldn't. What's that? I",
    "start": 182.879,
    "duration": 4.801
  },
  {
    "text": "can't hear you.",
    "start": 185.36,
    "duration": 5.36
  },
  {
    "text": "I said you'll have to speak up, Owl.",
    "start": 187.68,
    "duration": 6.639
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on. We've got work to do.",
    "start": 190.72,
    "duration": 6.32
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Uh, Mr. Owl.",
    "start": 194.319,
    "duration": 5.361
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Huh? What do you want?",
    "start": 197.04,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Could you help me with my bed?",
    "start": 199.68,
    "duration": 6.52
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Fine.",
    "start": 203.2,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "We're all set. Hooray!",
    "start": 208.879,
    "duration": 6.161
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks, Mr. Owl.",
    "start": 212.959,
    "duration": 4.721
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yes, good work, friend.",
    "start": 215.04,
    "duration": 4.24
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, it's time to gather the other",
    "start": 217.68,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": "forest critters. They're going to be so",
    "start": 219.28,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "happy to be rescued now. But the face",
    "start": 221.36,
    "duration": 5.12
  },
  {
    "text": "isn't even close to complete.",
    "start": 224.4,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Well, you've done such a good job so",
    "start": 226.48,
    "duration": 3.679
  },
  {
    "text": "far. Why don't you finish up here while",
    "start": 228.4,
    "duration": 3.759
  },
  {
    "text": "me and the kiddos gather the animals?",
    "start": 230.159,
    "duration": 4.561
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, hold on. That hardly seems",
    "start": 232.159,
    "duration": 4.881
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Hooray!",
    "start": 234.72,
    "duration": 6.519
  },
  {
    "text": "Right. Let's go, guys.",
    "start": 237.04,
    "duration": 4.199
  },
  {
    "text": "Thanks, friend. Good luck.",
    "start": 241.439,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Better get this base put together fast.",
    "start": 246.56,
    "duration": 6.92
  },
  {
    "text": "I don't like this.",
    "start": 249.519,
    "duration": 3.961
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 257.14,
    "duration": 3.16
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 267.16,
    "duration": 4.16
  },
  {
    "text": "Heat. Heat.",
    "start": 268.32,
    "duration": 3.0
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 277.3,
    "duration": 7.069
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 293.48,
    "duration": 17.81
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on, friends. Let's go home.",
    "start": 307.84,
    "duration": 5.919
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 311.29,
    "duration": 5.51
  },
  {
    "text": "There. All finished.",
    "start": 313.759,
    "duration": 6.321
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I told you, didn't I? Our new home.",
    "start": 316.8,
    "duration": 9.0
  },
  {
    "text": "Everyone, welcome. Meet Kasa as Sucasa.",
    "start": 320.08,
    "duration": 5.72
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 332.79,
    "duration": 3.129
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Dear monster.",
    "start": 334.88,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Owl, this place looks great, although",
    "start": 335.919,
    "duration": 7.201
  },
  {
    "text": "it's missing something. Oh, and what's",
    "start": 339.44,
    "duration": 4.319
  },
  {
    "text": "that?",
    "start": 343.12,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": ">> A proper entrance. Friends, help me whip",
    "start": 343.759,
    "duration": 4.081
  },
  {
    "text": "one up.",
    "start": 346.8,
    "duration": 4.61
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I I",
    "start": 347.84,
    "duration": 7.199
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 351.41,
    "duration": 6.44
  },
  {
    "text": ">> there. It's beautiful.",
    "start": 355.039,
    "duration": 6.241
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 357.85,
    "duration": 5.67
  },
  {
    "text": "Why is your face plastered on the front",
    "start": 361.28,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "when I did all the work? And",
    "start": 363.52,
    "duration": 7.119
  },
  {
    "text": "furthermore, wait, what are those?",
    "start": 365.919,
    "duration": 6.961
  },
  {
    "text": "Oh, the antlers. They look pretty good,",
    "start": 370.639,
    "duration": 7.801
  },
  {
    "text": "huh? Take them down, you idiot. Before",
    "start": 372.88,
    "duration": 5.56
  },
  {
    "text": ">> No. How could this have happened? I",
    "start": 385.6,
    "duration": 5.439
  },
  {
    "text": "tried to warn you about the coming",
    "start": 388.88,
    "duration": 5.599
  },
  {
    "text": "storm, but you didn't listen. Now, look",
    "start": 391.039,
    "duration": 6.641
  },
  {
    "text": "at what you have done to my face. Your",
    "start": 394.479,
    "duration": 6.481
  },
  {
    "text": "face? That's right. I'm doing what I",
    "start": 397.68,
    "duration": 6.16
  },
  {
    "text": "should have done a long time ago. Dear",
    "start": 400.96,
    "duration": 8.28
  },
  {
    "text": "monster, I exile you.",
    "start": 403.84,
    "duration": 5.4
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Wait, you can't kick him out. Where will",
    "start": 410.08,
    "duration": 2.959
  },
  {
    "text": "he go?",
    "start": 412.319,
    "duration": 3.121
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Doesn't matter to me. As long as he's",
    "start": 413.039,
    "duration": 5.761
  },
  {
    "text": "gone, you're welcome to go with him. No,",
    "start": 415.44,
    "duration": 5.28
  },
  {
    "text": "my friends are innocent. They shouldn't",
    "start": 418.8,
    "duration": 5.04
  },
  {
    "text": "suffer for my actions. I'll go. Just",
    "start": 420.72,
    "duration": 7.039
  },
  {
    "text": "please keep them safe.",
    "start": 423.84,
    "duration": 5.51
  },
  {
    "text": "Dear monster,",
    "start": 427.759,
    "duration": 4.7
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 429.35,
    "duration": 3.109
  },
  {
    "text": ">> what a mess. All right, people. We've",
    "start": 432.479,
    "duration": 5.521
  },
  {
    "text": "got a lot of work to do. Chop, chop.",
    "start": 435.599,
    "duration": 4.481
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What do we do now?",
    "start": 438.0,
    "duration": 4.319
  },
  {
    "text": ">> I guess we listen to the owl. The deer",
    "start": 440.08,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "meant well. But all this did happen",
    "start": 442.319,
    "duration": 5.921
  },
  {
    "text": "under his watch.",
    "start": 444.96,
    "duration": 6.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Stupid, stupid, stupid. How could it",
    "start": 448.24,
    "duration": 5.519
  },
  {
    "text": "have come to this? What was I thinking?",
    "start": 450.96,
    "duration": 6.88
  },
  {
    "text": "I put everyone in danger. I'm sorry.",
    "start": 453.759,
    "duration": 5.971
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Please. I'm sorry.",
    "start": 457.84,
    "duration": 3.12
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 459.73,
    "duration": 4.27
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Sorry. Won't bring your mother back. I",
    "start": 460.96,
    "duration": 4.639
  },
  {
    "text": "should have known you can never be a",
    "start": 464.0,
    "duration": 3.599
  },
  {
    "text": "protector. You can't even protect",
    "start": 465.599,
    "duration": 4.401
  },
  {
    "text": "yourself.",
    "start": 467.599,
    "duration": 4.961
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Dad was right. I'm not cut out to save",
    "start": 470.0,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "anyone. And now because of the rot,",
    "start": 472.56,
    "duration": 7.84
  },
  {
    "text": "because of me, it's hopeless. Help.",
    "start": 475.84,
    "duration": 8.6
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Huh? What was that?",
    "start": 480.4,
    "duration": 4.04
  },
  {
    "text": "Must have been my imagination. Somebody",
    "start": 485.52,
    "duration": 7.519
  },
  {
    "text": ">> that's coming from over here.",
    "start": 489.759,
    "duration": 6.601
  },
  {
    "text": ">> What the",
    "start": 493.039,
    "duration": 3.321
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 497.3,
    "duration": 3.139
  },
  {
    "text": "Please help",
    "start": 501.12,
    "duration": 4.479
  },
  {
    "text": "you. Don't just stand around watching.",
    "start": 503.199,
    "duration": 3.821
  },
  {
    "text": "Help me.",
    "start": 505.599,
    "duration": 3.201
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 507.02,
    "duration": 4.899
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You're right. Just hold tight.",
    "start": 508.8,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "Come on.",
    "start": 511.919,
    "duration": 4.0
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Yay. Going to pull my arms off. I",
    "start": 513.12,
    "duration": 4.159
  },
  {
    "text": "thought you were the guardian of the",
    "start": 515.919,
    "duration": 3.281
  },
  {
    "text": "forest. Isn't saving people your whole",
    "start": 517.279,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "thing.",
    "start": 519.2,
    "duration": 4.719
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Huh? You're right. It is. I am a",
    "start": 520.159,
    "duration": 7.68
  },
  {
    "text": "protector and I can't do this.",
    "start": 523.919,
    "duration": 8.04
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Wait. What's the plan?",
    "start": 527.839,
    "duration": 4.12
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 532.49,
    "duration": 3.059
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 541.01,
    "duration": 5.71
  },
  {
    "text": "Hey, are you okay? Uh,",
    "start": 543.839,
    "duration": 6.321
  },
  {
    "text": ">> oh my. Yes, just Peachy. Thanks to you.",
    "start": 546.72,
    "duration": 5.92
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact, since you saved me, I'll grant",
    "start": 550.16,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "you one wish.",
    "start": 552.64,
    "duration": 4.319
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Really? You can do that?",
    "start": 554.48,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": ">> From outside of that frog's belly, I",
    "start": 556.959,
    "duration": 4.32
  },
  {
    "text": "feel like I can do anything. Now, go on,",
    "start": 558.8,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "tell me what you desire. I want I want a",
    "start": 561.279,
    "duration": 5.441
  },
  {
    "text": "chance to make things right. For this",
    "start": 564.64,
    "duration": 4.48
  },
  {
    "text": "forest to go back to the way it was. For",
    "start": 566.72,
    "duration": 3.92
  },
  {
    "text": "all the creatures to have a safe and",
    "start": 569.12,
    "duration": 2.88
  },
  {
    "text": "happy home.",
    "start": 570.64,
    "duration": 3.68
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Well, that's the kind of three wishes,",
    "start": 572.0,
    "duration": 6.76
  },
  {
    "text": "but very well. Here we go.",
    "start": 574.32,
    "duration": 4.44
  },
  {
    "text": ">> Remarkable.",
    "start": 580.959,
    "duration": 4.56
  },
  {
    "text": ">> We're not done yet.",
    "start": 582.16,
    "duration": 5.76
  },
  {
    "text": ">> You've returned. What's the meaning of",
    "start": 585.519,
    "duration": 4.88
  },
  {
    "text": "this? I'm sorry for not trusting you,",
    "start": 587.92,
    "duration": 5.84
  },
  {
    "text": "Owl. I really made a mess of things. I",
    "start": 590.399,
    "duration": 7.511
  },
  {
    "text": "hope this will make it right.",
    "start": 593.76,
    "duration": 12.229
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 597.91,
    "duration": 8.079
  },
  {
    "text": "[Music]",
    "start": 608.13,
    "duration": 4.389
  }
]